      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for its next chapter and offers a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves. While it shows significant wear and will require some dedicated mechanical attention, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get started on a custom build or a great source for parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own today!",
